{
  "DARV.talk.ARKNIGHTS_MIZUKI_CHARACTER_MIZUKI.0-0.char": "哇，这里像是被潮水冲上来的仓库呢。每一件东西都留着一点来处的味道。",
  "DARV.talk.ARKNIGHTS_MIZUKI_CHARACTER_MIZUKI.0-0.next": "继续",
  "DARV.talk.ARKNIGHTS_MIZUKI_CHARACTER_MIZUKI.0-1.ancient": "好眼光！我收藏的不是破烂，是被时间腌过的宝物！挑吧，小海客！",
  "DARV.talk.ARKNIGHTS_MIZUKI_CHARACTER_MIZUKI.1-0r.ancient": "你又来了！我还给你留着几样不像给人类用的东西呢。哎呀，这说法是不是正合适？",
  "DARV.talk.ARKNIGHTS_MIZUKI_CHARACTER_MIZUKI.2-0.ancient": "你找东西的样子不像贪心，倒像在确认哪些东西还适合继续生长。",
  "DARV.talk.ARKNIGHTS_MIZUKI_CHARACTER_MIZUKI.2-0.next": "回应",
  "DARV.talk.ARKNIGHTS_MIZUKI_CHARACTER_MIZUKI.2-1.char": "能被带走的东西，多少都还有用处吧。连旧骨头也能给新芽一点养分。",
  "DARV.talk.ARKNIGHTS_MIZUKI_CHARACTER_MIZUKI.2-1.next": "继续",
  "DARV.talk.ARKNIGHTS_MIZUKI_CHARACTER_MIZUKI.2-2.ancient": "哈哈！那就拿去吧。别把我的宝贝全种进海里，至少留一件给塔听个响。",
  "NEOW.talk.ARKNIGHTS_MIZUKI_CHARACTER_MIZUKI.0-0.char": "你好。你的声音从很深的地方传来，像泡在水里的钟。",
  "NEOW.talk.ARKNIGHTS_MIZUKI_CHARACTER_MIZUKI.0-0.next": "继续",
  "NEOW.talk.ARKNIGHTS_MIZUKI_CHARACTER_MIZUKI.0-1.ancient": "[sine]...深处...也会...孵出...道路.....[/sine]",
  "NEOW.talk.ARKNIGHTS_MIZUKI_CHARACTER_MIZUKI.1-0r.ancient": "[sine]...孩子...又回到...起点.....\n...不是迷路...是潮汐.....[/sine]",
  "NEOW.talk.ARKNIGHTS_MIZUKI_CHARACTER_MIZUKI.2-0.ancient": "[sine]...你...想要...什么...？[/sine]",
  "NEOW.talk.ARKNIGHTS_MIZUKI_CHARACTER_MIZUKI.2-0.next": "祈求",
  "NEOW.talk.ARKNIGHTS_MIZUKI_CHARACTER_MIZUKI.2-1.char": "给我一颗还没有发芽的种子就好。它会不会长成树，我想亲眼看看。",
  "NEOW.talk.ARKNIGHTS_MIZUKI_CHARACTER_MIZUKI.2-1.next": "继续",
  "NEOW.talk.ARKNIGHTS_MIZUKI_CHARACTER_MIZUKI.2-2.ancient": "[sine]...去吧...\n...带着...未完成的...海.....[/sine]",
  "NONUPEIPE.talk.ARKNIGHTS_MIZUKI_CHARACTER_MIZUKI.0-0.char": "你的衣料真漂亮，像会自己选择光线。博士应该会说不要随便碰。",
  "NONUPEIPE.talk.ARKNIGHTS_MIZUKI_CHARACTER_MIZUKI.0-0.next": "继续",
  "NONUPEIPE.talk.ARKNIGHTS_MIZUKI_CHARACTER_MIZUKI.0-1.ancient": "那就让它更漂亮些！好孩子总该配一点能迷住命运的颜色。",
  "NONUPEIPE.talk.ARKNIGHTS_MIZUKI_CHARACTER_MIZUKI.1-0r.ancient": "你身上的颜色变多了，海蓝、月白、还有一点不好命名的危险。",
  "NONUPEIPE.talk.ARKNIGHTS_MIZUKI_CHARACTER_MIZUKI.2-0.ancient": "来吧，换上一层新光。就算你不属于人群，也该让人群记得你走过。",
  "NONUPEIPE.talk.ARKNIGHTS_MIZUKI_CHARACTER_MIZUKI.2-0.next": "婉拒",
  "NONUPEIPE.talk.ARKNIGHTS_MIZUKI_CHARACTER_MIZUKI.2-1.char": "我不太懂“惹人注目”的好处。靠近我的坏人，通常不会因为看清我而变好。",
  "NONUPEIPE.talk.ARKNIGHTS_MIZUKI_CHARACTER_MIZUKI.2-1.next": "继续",
  "NONUPEIPE.talk.ARKNIGHTS_MIZUKI_CHARACTER_MIZUKI.2-2.ancient": "哎呀，那就让好人看见你吧。美丽有时不是诱饵，是灯塔。",
  "OROBAS.talk.ARKNIGHTS_MIZUKI_CHARACTER_MIZUKI.0-0.char": "你这里好热闹。像电子游戏厅，只是会跳出来的东西更多。",
  "OROBAS.talk.ARKNIGHTS_MIZUKI_CHARACTER_MIZUKI.0-0.next": "继续",
  "OROBAS.talk.ARKNIGHTS_MIZUKI_CHARACTER_MIZUKI.0-1.ancient": "游戏厅！！我喜欢这个说法！！来，试试会咬人的奖品！！",
  "OROBAS.talk.ARKNIGHTS_MIZUKI_CHARACTER_MIZUKI.1-0r.ancient": "吃豆、吃药、吃命运！你很会玩嘛！！再来一局！！",
  "OROBAS.talk.ARKNIGHTS_MIZUKI_CHARACTER_MIZUKI.2-0.ancient": "送你一个声音！一个会在脑子里游来游去的声音！！",
  "OROBAS.talk.ARKNIGHTS_MIZUKI_CHARACTER_MIZUKI.2-0.next": "回应",
  "OROBAS.talk.ARKNIGHTS_MIZUKI_CHARACTER_MIZUKI.2-1.char": "谢谢。但如果它开始教我分辨谁该被吃掉，我可能要先把它吐出来。",
  "OROBAS.talk.ARKNIGHTS_MIZUKI_CHARACTER_MIZUKI.2-1.next": "继续",
  "OROBAS.talk.ARKNIGHTS_MIZUKI_CHARACTER_MIZUKI.2-2.ancient": "好！！谨慎也很有趣！！拿走它，让塔里多一点回声！！",
  "PAEL.talk.ARKNIGHTS_MIZUKI_CHARACTER_MIZUKI.0-0.char": "这里很安静。安静到能听见血肉慢慢适应新的形状。",
  "PAEL.talk.ARKNIGHTS_MIZUKI_CHARACTER_MIZUKI.0-0.next": "继续",
  "PAEL.talk.ARKNIGHTS_MIZUKI_CHARACTER_MIZUKI.0-1.ancient": "[thinky_dots]柔软的孩子……收下柔软的礼物……疼痛会变得很轻……[/thinky_dots]",
  "PAEL.talk.ARKNIGHTS_MIZUKI_CHARACTER_MIZUKI.1-0r.ancient": "[thinky_dots]你学会了把伤口当成门……门后面还有更深的水……[/thinky_dots]",
  "PAEL.talk.ARKNIGHTS_MIZUKI_CHARACTER_MIZUKI.2-0.ancient": "[thinky_dots]拿走我的血肉吧……它不会问你是谁……只会帮你继续活着……[/thinky_dots]",
  "PAEL.talk.ARKNIGHTS_MIZUKI_CHARACTER_MIZUKI.2-0.next": "回答",
  "PAEL.talk.ARKNIGHTS_MIZUKI_CHARACTER_MIZUKI.2-1.char": "活着很好。只是有些生命如果只顾自己延续，会把周围都吃空。",
  "PAEL.talk.ARKNIGHTS_MIZUKI_CHARACTER_MIZUKI.2-1.next": "继续",
  "PAEL.talk.ARKNIGHTS_MIZUKI_CHARACTER_MIZUKI.2-2.ancient": "[thinky_dots]那就带着它……学会不把一切吃空的活法……[/thinky_dots]",
  "TANX.talk.ARKNIGHTS_MIZUKI_CHARACTER_MIZUKI.0-0.char": "武器吗？我其实不擅长战斗。不过如果目标是坏人，博士会让我试试看。",
  "TANX.talk.ARKNIGHTS_MIZUKI_CHARACTER_MIZUKI.0-0.next": "继续",
  "TANX.talk.ARKNIGHTS_MIZUKI_CHARACTER_MIZUKI.0-1.ancient": "[b]不擅长也要拿稳！！善良没有牙齿，就只能被嚼碎！！[/b]",
  "TANX.talk.ARKNIGHTS_MIZUKI_CHARACTER_MIZUKI.1-0r.ancient": "[b]你比看上去锋利！这很好！！把犹豫磨掉，把敌人砍开！！[/b]",
  "TANX.talk.ARKNIGHTS_MIZUKI_CHARACTER_MIZUKI.2-0.ancient": "[b]别只想着分辨善恶！战场上先活下来，才有空继续思考！！[/b]",
  "TANX.talk.ARKNIGHTS_MIZUKI_CHARACTER_MIZUKI.2-0.next": "退让",
  "TANX.talk.ARKNIGHTS_MIZUKI_CHARACTER_MIZUKI.2-1.char": "嗯。我会活下来。毕竟还有很多料理、漫画和游戏没来得及尝。",
  "TANX.talk.ARKNIGHTS_MIZUKI_CHARACTER_MIZUKI.2-1.next": "继续",
  "TANX.talk.ARKNIGHTS_MIZUKI_CHARACTER_MIZUKI.2-2.ancient": "[b]好！！为了没尝过的世界而战，这理由足够响亮！！[/b]",
  "TEZCATARA.talk.ARKNIGHTS_MIZUKI_CHARACTER_MIZUKI.0-0.char": "闻起来很香。请问这些点心里有加过什么会改变生命结构的东西吗？",
  "TEZCATARA.talk.ARKNIGHTS_MIZUKI_CHARACTER_MIZUKI.0-0.next": "继续",
  "TEZCATARA.talk.ARKNIGHTS_MIZUKI_CHARACTER_MIZUKI.0-1.ancient": "哎呀，多懂行的小客人。放心，只有一点点[jitter][b]温暖[/b][/jitter]和一点点秘密。",
  "TEZCATARA.talk.ARKNIGHTS_MIZUKI_CHARACTER_MIZUKI.1-0r.ancient": "你尝东西的样子真认真，像在判断一颗星星能不能被做成汤。",
  "TEZCATARA.talk.ARKNIGHTS_MIZUKI_CHARACTER_MIZUKI.2-0.ancient": "来吧，吃点[jitter][b]甜的[/b][/jitter]。甜味能让很多尖锐的问题暂时变圆。",
  "TEZCATARA.talk.ARKNIGHTS_MIZUKI_CHARACTER_MIZUKI.2-0.next": "推辞",
  "TEZCATARA.talk.ARKNIGHTS_MIZUKI_CHARACTER_MIZUKI.2-1.char": "如果问题变圆之后就滚走了，答案也会不见吧？我还是想慢慢嚼。",
  "TEZCATARA.talk.ARKNIGHTS_MIZUKI_CHARACTER_MIZUKI.2-1.next": "继续",
  "TEZCATARA.talk.ARKNIGHTS_MIZUKI_CHARACTER_MIZUKI.2-2.ancient": "真挑剔。那就带走吧，等你愿意的时候再让它在舌尖融化。",
  "VAKUU.talk.ARKNIGHTS_MIZUKI_CHARACTER_MIZUKI.0-0.char": "契约听起来很像菜单。只是菜单通常不会要求食材签名。",
  "VAKUU.talk.ARKNIGHTS_MIZUKI_CHARACTER_MIZUKI.0-0.next": "继续",
  "VAKUU.talk.ARKNIGHTS_MIZUKI_CHARACTER_MIZUKI.0-1.ancient": "多新鲜的比喻。来吧，签下它，你就能得到一点[sine]更可靠的饥饿[/sine]。",
  "VAKUU.talk.ARKNIGHTS_MIZUKI_CHARACTER_MIZUKI.1-0r.ancient": "你看条款的眼神不像孩子，倒像在替某个生态圈审阅未来。",
  "VAKUU.talk.ARKNIGHTS_MIZUKI_CHARACTER_MIZUKI.2-0.ancient": "我可以卖给你一条捷径：从弱小，直接走向足以保护一切的强大。",
  "VAKUU.talk.ARKNIGHTS_MIZUKI_CHARACTER_MIZUKI.2-0.next": "回应",
  "VAKUU.talk.ARKNIGHTS_MIZUKI_CHARACTER_MIZUKI.2-1.char": "如果强大来得太快，我可能还没学会该保护谁、不该吞下谁。",
  "VAKUU.talk.ARKNIGHTS_MIZUKI_CHARACTER_MIZUKI.2-1.next": "继续",
  "VAKUU.talk.ARKNIGHTS_MIZUKI_CHARACTER_MIZUKI.2-2.ancient": "谨慎会让价格上涨。不过我喜欢你这种难卖的客人，拿去吧。",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.ARKNIGHTS_MIZUKI_CHARACTER_MIZUKI.0-0r.ancient": "你体内有两种秩序：一种学着做人，一种安静地等待扩散。你把哪一种称作自己？",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.ARKNIGHTS_MIZUKI_CHARACTER_MIZUKI.0-0r.next": "回答",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.ARKNIGHTS_MIZUKI_CHARACTER_MIZUKI.0-1r.char": "现在的话，应该是会听从博士指挥、也会想给大家做饭的那一种。",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.ARKNIGHTS_MIZUKI_CHARACTER_MIZUKI.0-1r.next": "继续",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.ARKNIGHTS_MIZUKI_CHARACTER_MIZUKI.0-2r.ancient": "答案温顺得近乎危险。越温顺的种子，越容易被人忽略它终将撑裂土壤。",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.ARKNIGHTS_MIZUKI_CHARACTER_MIZUKI.1-0r.ancient": "你又回来了。塔没有给你归属，却给了你足够多的实验条件。",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.ARKNIGHTS_MIZUKI_CHARACTER_MIZUKI.1-0r.next": "继续",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.ARKNIGHTS_MIZUKI_CHARACTER_MIZUKI.1-1r.char": "实验条件……听起来有点像罗德岛的体检室。只是这里更不担心受试者的感受。",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.ARKNIGHTS_MIZUKI_CHARACTER_MIZUKI.1-1r.next": "继续",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.ARKNIGHTS_MIZUKI_CHARACTER_MIZUKI.1-2r.ancient": "所以你该更诚实。你不是被观察的样本，你也是观察者。",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.ARKNIGHTS_MIZUKI_CHARACTER_MIZUKI.2-0r.ancient": "如果这座塔是一片封闭海域，你会让里面的生命彼此成全，还是让它们互相吞噬？",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.ARKNIGHTS_MIZUKI_CHARACTER_MIZUKI.2-0r.next": "继续",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.ARKNIGHTS_MIZUKI_CHARACTER_MIZUKI.2-1r.char": "我想先看清它们为什么这么做。然后，处理掉会让所有美好都消失的那一部分。",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.ARKNIGHTS_MIZUKI_CHARACTER_MIZUKI.2-1r.next": "继续",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.ARKNIGHTS_MIZUKI_CHARACTER_MIZUKI.2-2r.ancient": "很好。带着你的温和和裁决继续向上吧。二者相加，才是你的本相。",
  "ARKNIGHTS_MIZUKI_EVENT_LAST_TIDEWATCHER.title": "最后的观潮者",
  "ARKNIGHTS_MIZUKI_EVENT_LAST_TIDEWATCHER.epithet": "潮线尽头",
  "ARKNIGHTS_MIZUKI_EVENT_LAST_TIDEWATCHER.pages.INITIAL.description": "风暴在塔外停驻，海线像一条被拉直的伤口。高处的人影垂眼看向你，灯火、心脏、歌声与无名的遗产一并陈列在潮湿的石面上。\n\n“选择吧。走到这里的人，总该把自己剩下的部分交给某个答案。”",
  "ARKNIGHTS_MIZUKI_EVENT_LAST_TIDEWATCHER.pages.INITIAL.options.FIVE_RELICS.title": "听凭浪涌",
  "ARKNIGHTS_MIZUKI_EVENT_LAST_TIDEWATCHER.pages.INITIAL.options.FIVE_RELICS.description": "获得[gold]5[/gold]件随机遗物。",
  "ARKNIGHTS_MIZUKI_EVENT_LAST_TIDEWATCHER.pages.INITIAL.options.HEART.title": "献出所有",
  "ARKNIGHTS_MIZUKI_EVENT_LAST_TIDEWATCHER.pages.INITIAL.options.HEART.description": "失去所有金币，获得[gold]深蓝之心[/gold]。",
  "ARKNIGHTS_MIZUKI_EVENT_LAST_TIDEWATCHER.pages.INITIAL.options.THREE_RELICS.title": "听凭浪涌",
  "ARKNIGHTS_MIZUKI_EVENT_LAST_TIDEWATCHER.pages.INITIAL.options.THREE_RELICS.description": "随机获得[gold]3[/gold]件遗物。",
  "ARKNIGHTS_MIZUKI_EVENT_LAST_TIDEWATCHER.pages.INITIAL.options.SWAN_SONG.title": "记住绝唱",
  "ARKNIGHTS_MIZUKI_EVENT_LAST_TIDEWATCHER.pages.INITIAL.options.SWAN_SONG.description": "获得[gold]绝唱[/gold]。",
  "ARKNIGHTS_MIZUKI_EVENT_LAST_TIDEWATCHER.pages.INITIAL.options.LANTERN.title": "接过提灯",
  "ARKNIGHTS_MIZUKI_EVENT_LAST_TIDEWATCHER.pages.INITIAL.options.LANTERN.description": "获得[gold]提灯[/gold]。",
  "ARKNIGHTS_MIZUKI_EVENT_LAST_TIDEWATCHER.pages.DONE.description": "观潮者没有道别。你只听见浪声退去，又从更深处归来。",
  "ARKNIGHTS_MIZUKI_EVENT_LAST_TIDEWATCHER.talk.firstVisitEver.0-0.ancient": "你已经看见潮的尽头。那么，现在轮到潮看见你。",
  "ARKNIGHTS_MIZUKI_EVENT_LAST_TIDEWATCHER.talk.ANY.0-0r.ancient": "选吧。答案不会因为迟疑而变轻。",
  "ARKNIGHTS_MIZUKI_EVENT_LAST_TIDEWATCHER.pages.INITIAL.options.OCEAN_PULSE.title": "聆听脉搏",
  "ARKNIGHTS_MIZUKI_EVENT_LAST_TIDEWATCHER.pages.INITIAL.options.OCEAN_PULSE.description": "获得[gold]海洋的脉搏[/gold]。",
  "ARKNIGHTS_MIZUKI_EVENT_LAST_TIDEWATCHER.pages.INITIAL.options.ALL_ME.title": "众我归一",
  "ARKNIGHTS_MIZUKI_EVENT_LAST_TIDEWATCHER.pages.INITIAL.options.ALL_ME.description": "清除现有的排异反应与回响，获得一个独特的回响：[aqua]众我[/aqua]。"
}
